N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4810.6 - Registration as evidence of eligibility

State Regulations
A municipality shall make its own investigation and
determination of an applicant organization's eligibility for a license to
conduct bingo, as required by the Bingo Licensing Law, notwithstanding the
issuance of an identification number by the commission. Notes
